Categorial variables are two types 
1. Nominal :- order not matters 
   1. Onehotencoding:-  we can use pd.get_dummies method to create columns for each type one column will create 
                        Here we have concept called dummy variable tap we need to drop one column 
   2. Many categorial varaible 
   3. Mean encoding 
2. Ordinal :- Order matters 
   1. Label Encoder 
   2. Target Guided Encoding 

